One more bugfix and a new feature

title: - Adjusted: Added a comment regarding the new setTransparentBackground method in…
message:
- Adjusted: Added a comment regarding the new setTransparentBackground method in the README file as well as a hint for the new demo activity
- Adjusted: Added a java doc comment to the new demo activity for better understanding

title: - Added: A new activity for custom appearance was added with a new ip cam
message:
- Added: A new activity for custom appearance was added with a new ip cam
- Added: Two new icons for turning camera stream in custom appearance activity on and off were added
- Reverted: IpCamTwoActivity was set back to it's original 1.2.0 state
- Added: A new main activity for landscape orientation was added because with the default one some buttons weren't visible anymore because the list of buttons got too big
- Added: Beside the method to reset transparent background a new method is added to set the transparent background manually (which is needed when you reset the background for hiding purposes and then want to show the stream again with transparent background)

title: - Adjusted: README contains information about resetting transparent background…
message: - Adjusted: README contains information about resetting transparent background and clearing stream image now

title: - Implemented: New method to reset transparent background which is needed to…
message:
- Implemented: New method to reset transparent background which is needed to hide the view (ZOrder needs to be reverted and the format set back to default OPAQUE)
- Implemented: Method to clear the current drawn picture - This is useful when you hide and stop the stream and then turn it on because it first shows an old image
